Notes: WIAC Championship Final...Leading 13-11, UWW goes on a 19-1 run to take a
32-12 lead with 1:22 left in the second quarter...UWW led 51-20 with 2:05 left
in the third quarter...UWW's Trewyn has 19 points and 11 rebounds...UWO was
the three-time defending WIAC tournament champion.
